          "npcTexts": [ "Long enough. Why ask?", "I’m not planning to move." ],
          "isExit": false
        },
        {
          "playerText": "Have you noticed anything strange?",
          "npcTexts": [ "No. And if I did, it’s none of your business.", "I opened the door but saw no one…", "Someone must be asking for a beating."],
          "isExit": false
        },
        {
          "playerText": "What do you do for work?",
          "npcTexts": [ "Manual labor.", "Enough to live. Not your concern." ],
          "isExit": false
        },
        {
          "playerText": "When do you usually go out?",
          "npcTexts": [ "When I need to. Otherwise, I stay home.", "You ask too much." ],
          "isExit": false
        },
        {
          "playerText": "Goodbye.",
          "npcTexts": [ "Good.", "Leave me alone." ],
          "isExit": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
